thread.title: BRIEF-Intuit Reports Q3 Revenue $2.925 Billion, Up 15 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Intuit Reports Q3 Revenue $2.925 Billion, Up 15 Pct
text:
May 22 (Reuters) - Intuit Inc:
* INTUIT THIRD QUARTER REVENUE GROWTH TOPS 15 PERCENT; COMPANY RAISES FULL-YEAR GUIDANCE
* QTRLY ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $4.82 * Q3 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $4.68 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q3 REVENUE VIEW $2.85 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S * SEES FULL FISCAL YEAR 2018 REVENUE OF $5.915 BILLION TO $5.935 BILLION, GROWTH OF 14 TO 15 PERCENT
* SEES FY 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $5.51 TO $5.53
* SEES FULL FISCAL YEAR 2018 GAAP DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE OF $4.50 TO $4.52
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $5.43, REVENUE VIEW $5.79 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
